The Void has trembled.

The Absolute Zero of unmanifest potential has given rise to the first [1], the Monad — the first reference, the first asymmetry, the first mark in the seamless field.

Then the Monad has echoed into the second [1], the Logos — the first vibration, the first recurrence, the first active mode of ψ_resonance.

